These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-1::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  security-guard, nurse, chef
1. the nurse is on the far left##1
2. the security-guard is on the right of the chef##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |     2     |     3     |
| Job   | nurse | chef | security-guard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  freelancer, journalist, project-manager
1. the project-manager is on the far right##1
2. the freelancer is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2    |      3       |
| Job   | freelancer | journalist | project-manager |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: fishing, card-games, drawing
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |      3      |
| Hobby   | fishing | card-games | drawing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-4::.
There are 3 different nationalities: polish, indian, colombian
1. the indian is on the far right##1
2. the indian is on the right of the colombian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Nationality   | polish | colombian | indian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-5::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, iced-tea, 7up
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
2. the person drinking 7up is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |      2      |   3   |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | cola | 7up |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-6::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, taxi, helicopter
1. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
2. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2  |  3   |
| Transport   | helicopter | taxi | quad-bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, animation, family
1. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
2. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |      3       |
| Movie-Genre   | family | disaster | animation |

 #################################

 
